author: hsinweihsia
body: The BTV@HLT group has a Phase2 DeepJet retrained model. This PR is made to integrate the retrained DeepJet model into CMSSW. Please find the details in [7th HLT Upgrade Workshop](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1344917/#36-b-tagging-pog) and [here](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1393422/#3-round-robin-b-tagging-status).
title: Phase2 DeepJet retraining model integration to CMSSW
